scene.message:
Nanjo: Love is nothing more{nl}
than a fixed notion, don't{nl}
you think?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I bet there's a girl{nl}
out there secretly watching{nl}
me from the shadows too,{nl}
for sure...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: So that girl was a{nl}
Reiji fan, huh...{waitkey}Ah{wait_fr:21}, it's not like I'm{nl}
jealous or anything!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...{wait_fr:32}Can someone really{nl}
fall for another at just{nl}
one glance?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: ...{wait_fr:32}I don't understand{nl}
it. There's no need to get{nl}
so desperate over it.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey hey hey, what's{nl}
this? Isn't she a fan of{nl}
mine~?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: The boys at this school{nl}
are all so childish~ Ayase{nl}
isn't interested.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Sure, he seems grown-up{nl}
and all, but... Kido's a bit{nl}
off, isn't he.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: What? That woman's{nl}
glaring at me...{wait_fr:32} did I do{nl}
something?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Oh, senpai. Um...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
I saw a really cool guy just{nl}
now.{waitkey}It was a face I'd never seen,{nl}
so maybe he's a transfer{nl}
student...{waitkey}Ahh, who could he be...{waitkey}{ret}

Student: ...{wait_fr:21}Eek!{waitkey}Senpai, are you acquainted{nl}
with that person?{waitkey}Come on, introduce me,{nl}
please~{waitkey}{ret}
